channel.title: How do i make my server run!?!? i go to runserver and it says java is messed up
channel.description: HI. i m makeing a server called americanscape. so far i got all fikes ready all i need to do is make it not logg onto hybridscape! it loggs on throuhg my ip to regular moparscape? i asked how to make my server do that the guy said go to ur files and run ur server at runeserver.bat...so i did...and when i clicked the runserver file it said java is not a internal or external commmand, operate batch file...wtf is that???? how do i fix it???? this is so confusing it is probobly somthing simple but i never made a server b4....so will u plz help me out???..... :confused:

item.title: How do i make my server run!?!? i go to runserver and it says java is messed up
item.dc:creator: @BamBam BamBam
item.description:
@BamBam wrote:

make sure your java it up to date, right click and go to edit on both compile.bat and runserver.bat, make sure they set to to your correct java directory then try it again.
